---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Advertising Disclosure | CareCost Intelligence" description="Review how sponsorships, affiliate relationships, and ad placements are handled at CareCost Intelligence, including our rules for editorial independence and transparency.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Advertising Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="note">Updated: Feb 2026. We may earn revenue from ads or affiliate relationships.</p>
      <div class="tag">Last updated: Feb 2026</div>
      <div class="editorial-meta">Reviewed by CareCost Intelligence Editorial Team</div>
      <div class="author-box">
        <div class="author-title">Disclosure review</div>
        <div class="author-meta">
          <div>
            <strong>CareCost Intelligence Editorial Team</strong>
            <p class="note">This disclosure explains how advertising and affiliate relationships work. Read our <a href="/editorial-policy/">Editorial Policy</a> or <a href="/contact/">report a correction</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="chip-grid" style="margin-top: 12px;">
        <a class="chip" href="#ads">Advertising</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#affiliate">Affiliate links</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#labeling">Ad labeling</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#guardrails">Placement guardrails</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#data">Data and tracking</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#independence">Editorial independence</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#selection">Affiliate selection</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="ads">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p>We may display advertising to support free access to the site. Ads do not influence our cost modeling or planning guidance.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="affiliate">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
      <p>Some links may be affiliate links. If you click and take action, we may receive a commission at no additional cost to you.</p>
      <p class="note">We do not share personal care details with affiliates. If you choose to engage with a provider, you should verify terms directly with that provider.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="labeling">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Ad labeling and separation</h2>
      <p>We label advertising placements clearly and keep them separate from core planning guidance. Ads are designed to be identifiable so users can distinguish sponsored content from editorial content.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Sponsored placements are labeled and visually separated.</li>
        <li>Editorial content is produced independently of advertising.</li>
        <li>We avoid paid placement in checklists or estimator outputs.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="guardrails">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Placement guardrails</h2>
      <p>Advertising is limited to designated ad slots and is never inserted into estimator outputs, checklists, or quote workflows.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>No paid placements inside cost estimator results.</li>
        <li>No paid placement in state guide source lists.</li>
        <li>Ads must be clearly labeled and visually distinct.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="data">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Data and tracking</h2>
      <p>Advertising networks may use cookies or similar technologies to measure performance. We use this data to improve site usability and keep the site free to access.</p>
      <p class="note">You can review your browser privacy settings or use ad preference tools provided by your device or browser to manage ad personalization.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="independence">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Editorial independence</h2>
      <p>Our content is created to support planning accuracy and user outcomes. Sponsorship does not affect recommendations, rankings, or the tools we publish.</p>
      <p class="note">See our <a href="/editorial-policy/">Editorial Policy</a> for more detail.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="selection">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Affiliate selection</h2>
      <p>We prioritize partners that align with the planning needs of families and caregivers. Inclusion is not a guarantee of quality, and you should still validate services, pricing, and licensing independently.</p>
      <p class="note">If you believe a listing is inaccurate or misleading, contact us so we can review and correct it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="contact">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this disclosure can be sent to <a href="mailto:hello@carecostintel.com">hello@carecostintel.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
